# ============================================================
# NAME:    Rithmic
# TYPE:    Data Source (market data + trade execution)
# REPO:    https://github.com/kevshen13/surge-rules
# UPDATED: 2026-07-08
# USED BY: NinjaTrader, SierraChart, ATAS
# EXIT:    Route Rithmic to the SAME exit as the platform using it. Rithmic servers sit in the
#          CME Aurora (Chicago) data center -> a Chicago / US-East exit is geographically closest.
# NOTE:    LAN trading PCs proxy through Surge, so PROCESS-NAME does NOT apply to them; DOMAIN/IP rules route it.
# TODO:    Verify the IP ranges below against the CURRENT official Rithmic firewall advisory before relying on them.
# SOURCE:  Rithmic firewall advisory (R | Trade Execution Platform IP ranges + required ports).
# ============================================================

PROCESS-NAME,R Trader
PROCESS-NAME,R Trader Pro
PROCESS-NAME,R | Trader Pro
PROCESS-NAME,RTraderPro
PROCESS-NAME,Rithmic Trader
PROCESS-NAME,Rithmic Trader Pro
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,rithmic.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,rithmic.net
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,theomne.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,theomne.net
DOMAIN,paper.rithmic.com
DOMAIN,rithmicconnectivity.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,rithmicconnectivity.com

# Official Rithmic firewall advisory ports:
# TCP 65000/64100/63100/56000/55555/44444 and 40000-42099,
# UDP 45454.
IP-CIDR,38.65.202.192/27,no-resolve
IP-CIDR,38.65.210.64/28,no-resolve
IP-CIDR,38.79.0.80/28,no-resolve
IP-CIDR,38.98.144.224/27,no-resolve
IP-CIDR,128.177.47.161/28,no-resolve
IP-CIDR,130.117.187.64/28,no-resolve
IP-CIDR,184.104.190.17/28,no-resolve
IP-CIDR,184.105.22.224/27,no-resolve
IP-CIDR,216.57.156.160/28,no-resolve
